Building from git repository
============================

# Install build dependencies.

# Clone repository
git clone https://github.com/xypron/rkutils.git rkutils

# Move to target directory
cd rkutils/

# Update from git repository
git pull

# Create configure script
./autogen.sh

# Configure
./configure

# Make
./make -j6

# Test
./make check

# Install
sudo make install

